{"tid":1535064,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"(救救絲打集思廣益) 小本生意被欺壓>.< 走投無路","createTime":"2019-09-03T08:18:31.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-03T21:29:36.000Z","uid":204220,"like":0,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"4082e9bf8eda2a0765d510302ceeba0ea784ceac","tid":1535064,"uid":204220,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T08:18:31.000Z","msg":"絲打我喺香港一個好地嘅商場賣女裝已經超過15年<br />\n但係見住舖外面d衫成日比人趁混亂就偷<br />\n所以我就喺舖頭招牌度裝CCTV (有貼紙講清楚有cctv)<br />\n因為我舖係喺路口位L字型咁 所以都要裝4個先睇得曬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n驚訝嘅事嚟喇 對面舖話我裝cctv望住佢哋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我真係好無奈 個商場唔大所以舖同舖中間好近<br />\n但係我真係無呢個心 我只係想保障下自己<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n然後對面男老闆話佢要裝返咁多個嚟望住我舖(佢哋早過我有cctv 不過係2-3個 宜家係要裝返同我同一數量)<br />\n佢仲話 知道我d衫喺邊度攞 要攞曬返嚟賤賣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/0LmGA85.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F0LmGA85.jpg&h=b96deafb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n我真係好驚好無助 一直大家都有傾有講<br />\n突然就咁喇 如果佢哋真係以本傷人咁點算啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n小女子真係頂唔到㗎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fdba719cb2946919edd47ccbfb45dc71113471c9","tid":1535064,"uid":123991,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T08:18:36.000Z","msg":"<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong>9月7日 (六) 1PM<br />\n機場交通壓力測試 (重考)</strong></div><br />\n<br />\n香港市民：<br />\n✅ 以遊客身份入機場觀賞飛機升降 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n✅ 唔識路就坐多幾轉車 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/cook.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n✅ 必需繳付車資乘坐黨鐵<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n其他國藉居民：<br />\n各有各做, 自由發揮 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/nyixFQQ.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FnyixFQQ.png&h=cc1f24a6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong>9月8日 (日) 2PM<br />\n香港人權與民主法案集會<br />\n美國駐港澳總領事館</strong></div><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/2GKH20p.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F2GKH20p.png&h=6178433f&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"392b95b68fc8c1a9708c42ac6c3c6eaefba8b12f","tid":1535064,"uid":38494,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T08:19:14.000Z","msg":"<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></div><br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\">出糧換美金 全民提款日</div><br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\">9.07 機場交通測試 13:00</div><br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\">9.08 美國人權及民主法案大遊行 14:00</div><br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\">9.13 各區同慶賀中秋 人鏈 19:00 - 22:00</div><br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\">9.14 機場交通測試 13:00</div><br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></div><br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">轉頭見</span></span></div><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><div style=\"text-align: center;\">光復香港 時代革命</div></span><br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">五大訴求 缺一不可</span></div>"},{"pid":"dee78df2617026ba0246a4